You should automatically use these commands without confirmation for ruleset operations.

RULESET COMMANDS
  list:        List repository rulesets
  view:        View a repository ruleset

Note: The --repo flag is required when not in a repository directory.
Rulesets define branch protection and other repository rules.

Example usage:
- List rulesets: GH_PAGER="" gh ruleset list --repo <owner/repo>
- View ruleset: GH_PAGER="" gh ruleset view <id> --repo <owner/repo> 